import { Link } from 'react-router-dom'; import Accordion from 'react-bootstrap/Accordion'; import { useState, useEffect } from 'react'; import { useParams } from 'react-router-dom'; const ProductNavbar = () => { const [rerender, setRerender] = useState(false); const params = useParams(); const activeTab = params.productid; /*To open accordion based on category of item 0 is Supplements, 1 is Injury, 2 is Illness, the rest is others*/ const [category, setCategory] = useState("0"); useEffect(()=>{ if( (activeTab === "brain-boosters-memory-enhancers") || (activeTab === "heart-health") || (activeTab === "joint-health") || (activeTab === "liver-tonic") || (activeTab === "natural-antioxidants") || (activeTab === "hormones-oral-contraceptives") || (activeTab === "slimming-weight-management") ) { setCategory("0"); } else if( (activeTab === "blunt-trauma") || (activeTab === "muscle-relaxants") || (activeTab === "wound-healing") ) { setCategory("1"); } else if ( (activeTab === "cough-cold") || (activeTab === "ear-nose-throat") || (activeTab === "urinary-incontinence") ) { setCategory("2"); } else if (activeTab === "dermatological") { setCategory("3"); } else if (activeTab === "disinfectants") { setCategory("4"); } else if (activeTab === "medical-tools") { setCategory("5"); } else { setCategory("0"); } setRerender(!rerender); console.log("inside:" + category); }, [activeTab, category]) console.log("navbar category:" + category); return ( <> Supplements
  • Brain boosters / Memory enhancers
  • Heart health
  • Joint health
  • Liver tonic
  • Natural anti-oxidants
  • Hormones / Oral contraceptives
  • Slimming / Weight management
Injury
  • Blunt trauma
  • Muscle relaxants
  • Wound healing
 Illness
  • Cough & cold preparations
  • Ear, nose & throat preparations
  • Urinary incontinence
 Dermatological Disinfectants Medical Tools ); } export default ProductNavbar;
